svg.text: Honeyz is the first metaverse fashion doll, we are a community of 10,000 fashion forward women who are owning the blockchain runway.

Honeyz is building a lasting community driven around fashion and web3. We are excited to be supporting non-profit organizations that align with our mission to educate & empower women in tech and web3.
5% of our primary sales and 10% of our secondary will be donated to organizations that support women in tech and crypto.
How are you supporting the community?
2.5% of primary sales and 5% of net secondary sales will be sent to a community wallet. These funds will be used to invest in emerging women lead NFT projects.
